  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK931">
<l>vēṇṭaṟka veṉṟiṭiṉuñ cūtiṉai veṉṟatūum </l>
<l> tūṇṭiṟpoṉ mīṉviḻuṅki yaṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Though able to win, let not one desire gambling; (for) even what is won is like a fish swallowing the iron in fish-hook.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
